(20, 1482, 4, 'manjiri', 'Affordable healthcare services ', 'healthcare_banner_6892625911.jpg', 'health_6892625921.png', '<p>Services: we offer a wide range of medical services to address the diverse needs of our patients. Our team of skilled healthcare professionals includes doctors, nurses, specialists, and support staff, all working together to deliver exceptional care. Our services include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>General Medicine: We provide primary care services, including routine check-ups, preventive care, vaccinations, and treatment for common illnesses.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Specialized Care: Our clinic offers specialized care in various fields such as cardiology, dermatology, gastroenterology, gynecology, orthopedics, pediatrics, and more. Our dedicated specialists provide expert diagnosis, treatment, and ongoing management of specific health conditions.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Diagnostic Services: We have state-of-the-art diagnostic facilities equipped with advanced technology. Our diagnostic services include laboratory testing, imaging services (X-rays, ultrasounds, CT scans), ECGs, and other necessary investigations to aid accurate diagnosis.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Urgent Care: For non-life-threatening emergencies, our clinic offers prompt and efficient urgent care services. Our medical professionals are trained to handle a wide range of urgent medical conditions, providing immediate treatment and relief.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Chronic Disease Management: We specialize in managing chronic diseases such as diabetes, hypertension, asthma, and more. Our healthcare team develops personalized treatment plans, monitors progress, and provides ongoing support to improve patients&#39; quality of life.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Wellness Programs: We believe in preventive care and offer wellness programs to promote healthy lifestyles. These programs may include health screenings, nutrition counseling, weight management, smoking cessation support, and other initiatives aimed at disease prevention and health promotion.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '9664686756 / 0222 555446677', 'www.manjiriclinic..com', '<p><strong>Timing : 10.00 a.m to 7.00 p.m&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n', '23,25', '32,36,38,39,40,51,54', '', '', '', '1', '2023-06-20 14:35:47', 0);
