(258, 1, '7 Days Challenge', '', 0, 0, 0, '1', 'img-a123_40128129.jpeg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Are you ready to push yourself to new limits and unlock your full potential? L</strong>ook no further! Proceed.Fit is thrilled to present <strong>the 7-Day Challenge</strong>, a transformative journey designed to elevate your mental and physical fitness to extraordinary heights.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The 7-Day Challenge is a comprehensive program that combines physical fitness, mental resilience, and personal growth. It is a commitment to yourself and your well-being for 75 days straight, pushing you beyond your comfort zone and instilling discipline, determination, and perseverance.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">This challenge is for those who are ready to embrace change and transform their lives. Here&#39;s what you can expect from the 7-Day Challenge.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Prizes</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Each month, we will select 10 participants who have successfully completed and consistently logged their activities for all 75 days of the challenge, achieving an average score above 95%. These 10 participants will be awarded an exclusive 7-Day Challenge T-shirt as a recognition of their dedication and achievement.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\